Anyways Robert Jordan was positively great the first 5 books, he really can develop characters.  But going on book 9 (or is it 10) how much more can you describe characters.  This last one was definitely a stalling piece, at some times I even wonder if it wasn't ghost written.  The style seems to have changed from the original.<br>
